      <paragraph>The Qt XML Patterns module provides support for XPath, <link href="xmlprocessing.html">XQuery</link>, XSLT and XML Schema validation.</paragraph>
      <paragraph>The <link href="qtxmlpatterns-index.html">Qt XML Patterns</link> module provides support for XPath, <link href="xmlprocessing.html">XQuery</link>, XSLT and XML Schema validation.</paragraph>
